              <div id="raid-mit-new-desc-hint" class="govuk-hint">Use “We are” or “We will” language. Must be funded and resourced.</div>
              <textarea class="govuk-textarea govuk-!-width-full" id="raid-mit-new-desc" name="title" rows="5" maxlength="450" aria-describedby="raid-mit-new-desc-hint" placeholder="e.g. We will implement multi-AZ cloud redundancy"></textarea>
